  retrievalError       String?
  // 68.md P9 round 2 — sha256 of the file bytes for content-level dedupe (the OA
  // worker previously deduped by sourceUrl only). Nullable + plain index: additive
  // db-push-safe on this EXISTING table; legacy rows stay null.
